{"tid":1978720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三次遊行 越打壓越反抗","createTime":"2020-04-19T02:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T03:01:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"672d1c4e4ec669277e99be5352bf98a8d06ef06a","tid":1978720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200419/7YYKEED4TBKYYRMI5Y4JVQZROU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200419%2F7YYKEED4TBKYYRMI5Y4JVQZROU%2F&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=5ed522f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200419%2F7YYKEED4TBKYYRMI5Y4JVQZROU%2F&h=25deba2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200419/7YYKEED4TBKYYRMI5Y4JVQZROU/</a><br />\n<br />\n三次遊行 越打壓越反抗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200419/large/1587228543_2dca.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200419%2Flarge%2F1587228543_2dca.gif&h=ff38df99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【10.20 廢除惡法、獨立調查、重組警隊 九龍遊行】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】三次不被批准的遊行，三次抗命，展現港人「流水革命」的靈活和堅持，時而溫柔、時而激烈。同時反映政府面對無法阻擋的民意，只顧用每況愈下手段作出恐嚇，從不正視。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「民主祖父」首被控 查理斯97憂慮成真 彭定康：埋葬兩制新一步<br />\n<br />\n政權鎮壓 開真槍打青年<br />\n<br />\n去年8月，香港的逆權運動陷入一個小低潮。經過兩個多月持續抗爭，依然無法撼動政權半分，港人略現疲態，在機場的集會中更顯抗爭者進退失據。民陣號召港人在18日來一次大集氣，警方卻只准集會不准遊行。<br />\n<br />\n但聰明的港人發揮「如水」精神，從四面八方湧入維園參與流水式集會。那天，在暴雨下，雨傘開遍半個港島，遊行人潮順流遇上逆流，久久不進不退，但縱使雨水濕透雙腳，行人仍默默向維園蠕行。那天，勇武卸下裝備融入人群，與和理非相擁，170萬和勇合流，以耐性和溫柔為接下來的抗爭打一支強心針。<br />\n<br />\n惟政權毫不珍惜港人再度展現的和平，繼續對五大訴求充耳不聞，反以更惡劣的武力壓迫港人。警方8月25日響起第一槍實彈，再在8.31太子站內重演7.21白衣人暴行。林鄭縱在9月4日宣佈撤回送中條例，一切已太少太遲。<br />\n<br />\n「沒有國慶，只有國殤。」在10.1港人的國殤日中，民主派不理政權反對照舊上街，港人亦展現敢於抗命的勇氣，在各區發起大型示威。為保中共執政70年的面子，政權以最高的武力打壓，單日發射六槍實彈，其中一發更打入一名年輕示威者的胸口。港人抗爭的鮮血掩蓋虛假盛世，世界的目光都留意着香港。<br />\n<br />\n公權力無法退卻港人的抗爭意志，極權就轉以更卑劣的手段，派出南亞刀手襲擊民陣召集人岑子杰至重傷。但港人再度展現打不死的鬥志及對種族的包容。10.20多達35萬人在少數族裔同行下上街抗命。警方當日亂射水炮玷污清真寺與聖安德烈堂，暴露了警隊的野蠻。<br />\n<br />\n三次遊行，港人一再以行動宣示，生來自有遊行集會自由，毋須政權批准亦無法阻止。乘人之危不義，政權在港人集中抗疫的時候秋後算賬，林鄭月娥又怎能讓港人信服？<br />\n<br />\n■記者關冠麒"},{"pid":"dc607e6ba8f09d8cf1f6de68fa0fb6be2535fb50","tid":1978720,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:30:35.000Z","msg":"快一國一制啦<br />\n等大家唔洗遊行"},{"pid":"817861dd6311622b5c4b233ed8d75d169aa6060e","tid":1978720,"uid":80396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:44:51.000Z","msg":"最記得有個勇武舉牌，有個呀叔過去抱住佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debbf398ba439a69b0b0763ca002084ed99d748e","tid":1978720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"817861dd6311622b5c4b233ed8d75d169aa6060e","tid":1978720,"uid":80396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02:44:51.000Z","msg":"最記得有個勇武舉牌，有個呀叔過去抱住佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T03:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和勇不分"}]}